      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>2nd-level druid @variantrule[optional class features|tce|optional feature]</i></p><p>You gain the ability to summon a spirit that assumes an animal form: as an action, you can expend a use of your Wild Shape feature to cast the @UUID[Compendium.renegados-compendium.magias.Item.KPmL9LiJ0dfpThSj] spell, without material components.</p><p>When you cast the spell in this way, the familiar is a fey instead of a beast, and the familiar disappears after a number of hours equal to half your druid level.</p></div>",
